success.question_text:
Which two of the following statements together prove that:

SOME VERTEBRATES LAY EGGS?

I. Reptiles lay eggs.

II. Brown snakes are reptiles.

III. Brown snakes are vertebrates.

IV. Reptiles are vertebrates.

review_1.column_1_text:

(I and IV) Reptiles lay eggs. Reptiles are vertebrates.
